quran[4]{c,v,t}:
  112,1,"Dheh: Allaah waa Mid Keliya (Axad ah aan wax shariig ah lahayn)."
  112,2,"Allaah waa Sayidka Deeqtoon (ma baahdaha loo wada baahan yahay)."
  112,3,"Ma dhalin96676&gt;2, lamana dhalin",footnotes:&lt;sup:3
  112,4,"Ma jiro axad u dhigma (Alle oo la mid ah ama la barbar dhigo)."
